<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-responsible-for">be responsible for</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>对……负责</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Human activity is not responsible for all water shortages.
水资源短缺不完全是由人类活动造成的。</p><footer>2013 安徽</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He takes the view that children are responsible for their own actions.
他的观点是孩子应对自己的行为负责。</p></div></div>